Instagirl, l3n0v0â€¦ a girl with silky silver hair tied into a high ponytail, loose strands brushing her cheeks. Her eyes are icy blue, sharp and alert. She wears a cropped leather biker jacket over a fitted black camisole, distressed denim shorts with fishnet tights peeking through, and heavy lace-up boots with metallic buckles. A choker with a dangling crystal catches the light at her throat.
She leans against a graffiti-covered brick wall in an underground subway station, the tiled ceiling glowing with harsh fluorescent lights. A train rushes past in the background, streaks of motion blur cutting across the frame. She tilts her head slightly, one eyebrow raised, her expression equal parts daring and playful.
